      dct:description "Pitch-reframe strategy synthesis review session, May 21 2026. Scarlet resolves the apparent tension between the B2C primary market claim and the enterprise-centered Tranche-1 ICP by establishing that Expert, Team, and Org tiers are a continuum of one use case, not distinct markets." ;
